X-Chat Requirements:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   - GNU MAKE    (get it from ftp://ftp.gnu.org)
   - GTK 1.2.0+  (get it from http://www.gtk.org)

 Optional:

   - Gnome (1.00 or above only)     (http://www.gnome.org)
   - Perl                           (http://www.perl.com)
   - Python                         (http://www.python.org)


X-Chat Compiling and Installation
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Type this:

	./configure
	gmake

Become root and type:

	gmake install


Other Options
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

If you do not have GNU Gettext installed, instead use:

	./configure --disable-nls


If you want to disable Gnome and/or Perl you can do:

	./configure --disable-perl --disable-gnome


If you want to enable use of SOCKS5 do:

	./configure --enable-socks


If you want to install a smaller stripped binary (without debug) do:

	gmake install-strip
